select * from ( select '1' as chart_id, 'school-wise student attendance percentage' as chart_name ,school_id as x_axis, round(total_present*100.0/total_working_days,2) as x_value, 'latitude' as y_axis,school_latitude as y_value,'longitude' as z_axis ,school_longitude as z_value,year,month from school_student_total_attendance ) as p where x_value<=100
